            <thetext>We use the &quot;variants&quot; optimization to minimize the dependencies (and thus file size) of stand-alone low-level libraries. We would like to additionally provide uncompressed versions of these libraries but the variants optimization always includes code compression.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
