            <thetext>I&#39;ve introduced a new optimization, &quot;whitespace&quot;, that is solely responsible 
for compressing whitespace. Other optimizations will not trigger this anymore, 
so it has to be added explicitly to any other optimization if it is wanted.

&quot;whitespace&quot; has also been added to the default optimizations in base.json. I 
will add it to other config files where necessary.

master: 7560024</thetext>
